des: Here at Game Changing Dads we know how tough it is to stay motivated to be a good father and husband. Each week we bring you honest and real discussions on how to lead, love, and live! Let Game Changing Dads show you how to take charge of your leadership role and help you learn to juggle the demands of your career and personal life. Our goal here at GCD is to help you focus on what should be your first priority, FAMILY!
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
